본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 rehabilitation medicine (PMR physiatry — 외상/뇌졸중/MS/Parkinson/뇌성마비/절단/호흡/이식/노인/소아 후 회복 약리 + device adjuvant) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_sci` (SCI specific) + `.roadmap.disease_stroke_acute` (acute reperfusion) + `.roadmap.disease_neurodegen` (chronic): rehabilitation medicine = PMR physiatry framework + 재활 약리 broad — spasticity post-injury motor learning + post-stroke aphasia + post-injury cognitive + assistive device + brain-computer interface adjuvant. dalfampridine + amantadine + modafinil + intrathecal baclofen + BoNT 6-serotype + neuromuscular electrical stimulation 약리 supplementary.)

