## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **dalfampridine ER Ampyra 2010** = first FDA MS walking — Kv1.x potassium channel block. research SCI/stroke 적응증 확장. quantum-VQE 의 K-channel pocket leverage.
2. **amantadine 1968+ TBI 회복 + Parkinson + 인지 자극** = NMDA open-channel block + dopamine release. dual mechanism — 50+ year drug 의 재활 paradigm 회복. hxq-rehab-amantadine-002 = next-gen.
3. **BoNT 6-serotype 1989+** = onabotulinumtoxinA + abobotulinumtoxinA + incobotulinumtoxinA + prabotulinumtoxinA 2019 + daxibotulinumtoxinA Daxxify 2022 longer-duration + rimabotulinumtoxinB. focal spasticity post-stroke/CP/TBI 재활 표준. SNARE protease quantum-VQE leverage.
4. **intrathecal baclofen pump (Lioresal/Gablofen) 1996** = severe spasticity 지속-방출. oral baclofen 중추 부작용 회피. WEAVE pump device + GABA-B agonist combined.
5. **modafinil + armodafinil + methylphenidate + lisdexamfetamine** = TBI/MS/SCI/post-stroke fatigue + 인지 재활 4-drug class. dopamine/norepinephrine modulator + amphetamine prodrug. quantum-VQE 의 DAT/NET pocket leverage.
6. **nuedexta dextromethorphan/quinidine 2010** = pseudobulbar affect (post-stroke + MS + ALS) — σ1 + NMDAR. emotion incontinence 재활 표준. quantum-VQE 의 σ1 pocket fit.
7. **VMAT2 tetrabenazine + deutetrabenazine 2017 + valbenazine 2017** = chorea + tardive dyskinesia 재활 표준. Huntington 외 cross-rehab. quantum-VQE 의 VMAT2 pocket selectivity.
8. **citicoline (Spain/JP std) + piracetam (EU/동유럽) US 미승인** = post-stroke 회복 + 인지 재활. US-non-FDA 임상 paradigm 차이. cross-jurisdiction rehab pharmacology.
9. **BCI Neuralink/Synchron/Blackrock + exoskeleton Ekso/ReWalk/Indego + VR MindMaze** = device adjuvant. drug 보다 device-driven motor restoration. cross-digital_therapeutics + 재활.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, rehabilitation medicine 임상 의미 한정. erythropoietin TBI/SCI Phase 3 negative + 3K3A-APC + minocycline research-only = realistic translational gap.

